snippet.title: PokeMMO - It's what you think it is
snippet.description:
Welcome to a new era of online monster battles.
So stop playing with yourself and start playing with everyone else.

The Mod: https://pokemmo.eu/downloads/
3D Models: https://forums.pokemmo.eu/index.php?/topic/74169-modanimated-battle-sprites20200905/
